menu "E-Paper Display Configuration"

    config EP_DRIVER_SPECTRA_E6
        bool "Spectra E6 (7.3 Inch: Waveshare/reTerminal)"
        help
            Driver for 7.3 inch Spectra 6 E-Paper displays (Waveshare, Seeed reTerminal E1002).
            This board typically includes an AXP2101 PMIC and/or SD Card slot.

    config EP_DRIVER_SEEEDSTUDIO_T133A01
        bool "Seeed XIAO EE02 (13.3 Inch)"
        help
            Driver for Seeed Studio XIAO EE02 board with 13.3 inch Spectra 6 display.
            This board does NOT have an AXP PMIC or SD Card slot.

endmenu
